gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 141, Pelicans 117
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Pelicans, 141-117. Giannis Antetokounmpo led the way for the Bucks with a game-high 30 points, along with 12 rebounds and four assists, while Damian Lillard (26 points, six rebounds, nine assists) and Brook Lopez (24 points, six 3PM) added a combined 50 points in the victory. Brandon Ingram tallied 26 points and six rebounds for the Pelicans in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 32-14 on the season, while the Pelicans fall to 26-20.
